title: Bulldog Puppy Steals His Mom’s Sock And Where He Takes It Is Too Adorable
text:
Bulldog Puppy Steals His Mom’s Sock And Where He Takes It Is Too Adorable   
When it comes to socks, Pablo the Bulldog is pretty sure they are all his, even when they’re on his mom’s foot. In this adorable clip, the cute puppy grabs hold of his mom’s sock and won’t let go. Where he takes it next made me smile so much!
